      <guid>http://godliness.github.io/technology/keepalived-install/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;安装keepalived&#34;&gt;安装Keepalived&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&#34;下载源码包&#34;&gt;下载源码包&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;wget http://www.keepalived.org/software/keepalived-1.3.6.tar.gz
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&#34;解压源码包&#34;&gt;解压源码包&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;tar zxvf ./keepalived-1.3.6.tar.gz
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&#34;安装&#34;&gt;安装&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code&gt;yum install -y openssl-devel libnl3-devel ipset-devel iptables-devel libnfnetlink-devel
cd keepalived-1.3.6/
./configure --prefix=/usr/local/keepalived
make &amp;amp;&amp;amp; make install
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
